column49: The high refractory oil is formulated with bouncy gel for thicker 3D drop glow.The product tip is designed to perfectly adhere on your lips with delicate amount control and thick and even application.Provides an excellent pigmentation with single use without any darkening. The clear and vivid shade provides moisturizing and comfortable application on your lips to show new standards of glow lips.

column49: Minnie and 3CE watercolor makeup completed with the new Blur Water Tint.A fluffy, fixing lip that blurs like a blooming petal.Sweep onto lips for a watery first touch, then blend into the lips for a blurred finish that's less smudgeable and more moisturizing.
